        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>No Tax Subsidies for E-Cigarette and Tobacco Ads Act</strong></p> <p>This bill denies a tax deduction for expenses relating to direct-to-consumer advertising of tobacco products, including electronic nicotine delivery systems. </p>]]></text>
